{
  "stem": "12447.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We got to the roof.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We made our way through the roof.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we went into a building on the other side.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we waited in the staircase until dawn, until the curfew would, would finish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I remember it was very quiet, but kind of scary, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I would probably prefer to be in the street than sitting in that stairwell over there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But we got through that night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "In the morning, we started to walk toward the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was the Warszawa Glowna, what they call it in Polish, the general-- the main central railroad of Warsaw-- railroad station.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we got over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There were thousands of people traveling in all kinds of directions.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we got in line.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we waited to, to get a ticket.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was really hard to get a ticket.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "People were pushing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And there were Polish policeman and a German policeman-- black uniform.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "That-- they were kind of keeping order and keeping the line going.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And there was always somebody that cut, cut in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Whatever it was, I stood there for a couple hours with my aunt trying to get to buy a ticket.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And a German [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] policeman, the one that was from the railroad-- the black uniforms-- they called them Bahnschutz.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He kind of started to play around with my aunt, flirting with her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They-- she made believe she don't understand what he's talking.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he couldn't speak Polish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But he was kind of getting, getting cute with her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And the Polish policeman occasionally would come and translate for them words here and there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But he wouldn't leave her alone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after a while, she told me that she-- she'll be right back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She walked away.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
